{"type": "article", "id": 23080, "title": "房子要是有很多边边角角，怎么把它们用起来？", "description": "因为形状不规则而像是“边角料”的空间，却变成不期而遇的惊喜。", "date": "2016-03-02T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 145, "name": "办公"}, {"id": 971, "name": "空间"}, {"id": 24208, "name": "设计工作室"}, {"id": 24209, "name": "DIG architects"}], "category": 17, "author": 451727, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 200, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607191347naHbLh9ZG1zyxs26.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>日本建筑师工作室 DIG Architects 为小型设计公司 BLUES DESGIN 设计了一个办公室，项目在日本名古屋的郊区的一栋体量不大的独栋物业。</p>\n<p>作为一个设计工作室，除了电子绘图桌、建模工作坊、会议室这类基础功能空间，更需要促进交流、头脑风暴和休闲放松这些激发想象力的空间。</p>\n<p>于是设计师在设计思路上打破了传统空间连续性。整个建筑的外型极其不规则，如此一来，室内便莫名“多出”一些空间来。设计师又采用了不同的方式，包括衔接室内和室外空间，设置过渡区，用装置连接交错的空间等，让这些形状不规则的“边角料”空间变成了让人意外的空间惊喜。</p>\n<p>“横看成岭侧成峰，远近高低各不同。”整个建筑外型不规则，门窗各自有不同的视野。</p>\n<p class=\"\">中国人或许不太喜欢这种不规整的空间，通常会认为风水不佳。不过你要是不信这些东西，这倒是一个很不错的利用不规则空间的参考。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607191340Zfti6UK5gpnoSqCs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>不规则的门口。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607191341u92O5MAK7XUS8CHG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50122249\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">由室外进入室内的过渡。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607191341uPYqlkSV6i93Lj0a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>不规则地安置了办公桌。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071913428CK0LPFvaA4DON2r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071913438vQeEXWo61gjS7HZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>休息区的桌子和墙在两条相交的线上，与室外空间相连。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607191344qCNBQToMxjJGE4Ut.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">“边角料空间”的景观布置。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607191344CjpcfJZwhBGIU0TS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>各种台阶将空间连接起来。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071913457z8h2dfeCx04g5uO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50122249\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">屋顶露台上还见缝插针地设了一个室外的浴缸。<br></p>\n<p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607191345kP0NiysdgOw7rVzx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">平面图</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607191346gL4mdEXVUSinvDCT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82518337\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">剖面图</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071913465h0feQxCascZORYz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64914425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图和文内图来自 <a href=\"http://www.ignant.de/2016/02/29/a-minimal-design-office-in-japan-by-dig-architects/?lang=de\">IGNANT</a>、<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/dig-architects-office-blues-design-02-10-2016/\">designboom</a>、<a href=\"http://www.dig-arch.com/top/work/peji/BLUES_DESIGN_office.html\">D.I.G Architects</a><br></p>\n\n\n"}